183
00:12:32,070 --> 00:12:33,070
Nothing serious.

184
00:12:38,590 --> 00:12:40,120
It's good that you're back.

185
00:12:40,470 --> 00:12:40,950
Mother,

186
00:12:42,040 --> 00:12:42,920
I will definitely

187
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:44,160
