236
00:15:05,930 --> 00:15:07,160
why did you bring

237
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:08,440
the God of Fortune too?

238
00:15:08,760 --> 00:15:10,270
I guess

239
00:15:10,290 --> 00:15:11,890
it's something you cherish.

240
00:15:12,180 --> 00:15:13,240
