274
00:16:33,110 --> 00:16:34,640
you've got what you wanted.

275
00:16:35,780 --> 00:16:37,450
I wanted to stay here for a few more days,

276
00:16:37,450 --> 00:16:38,380
but the people in Furong

277
00:16:38,380 --> 00:16:39,580
