281
00:16:50,740 --> 00:16:52,760
I heard you've become an Imperial Merchant.

282
00:16:52,760 --> 00:16:54,560
Furong is a more dangerous place

283
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,950
compared to Linchun.

284
00:16:56,390 --> 00:16:57,830
